content.problem:
Express the limit 
$\displaystyle\lim_{n\to\infty}\sum_{i=1}^{n}\sin\!\left(\frac{i\pi}{n}
\right)\frac{\pi}{n}$ as a definite integral.

marginNotes.text:
If I go up to the heavens, you are there; 
if I make my bed in the depths, you are there. If I rise on the wings 
of the dawn, if I settle on the far side of the sea…
